<section id="1002Z_S001S" variety="S001S">
<name>SLIDING ROOF</name>
<ttl id="1002Z_S001S_732XN_T00GB" variety="T00GB">
<name>SLIDING ROOF SYSTEM</name>
<para id="RM0000029GH003X" category="C" type-id="8020Y" name-id="RF07E-01" from="200601">
<dtccode>B2342</dtccode>
<dtcname>Switch Failure</dtcname>
<subpara id="RM0000029GH003X_01" type-id="60" category="03" proc-id="RM0250U___0000C5900000">
<name>DESCRIPTION</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>This DTC is output when the sliding roof drive gear sub-assembly (sliding roof control ECU) detects that the OPEN, CLOSE, UP or DOWN switch in the roof console box assembly (sliding roof control switch) is stuck for 30 seconds or more.</ptxt>
<table pgwide="1">
<tgroup cols="3">
<colspec colname="COL1" align="center" colwidth="1.42in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="2.83in"/>
<colspec colname="COL3" colwidth="2.83in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>DTC No.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>DTC Detection Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Trouble Area</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>B2342</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Sliding roof drive gear sub-assembly (sliding roof control ECU) detects OPEN, CLOSE, UP or DOWN switch in overhead junction block is stuck for 30 seconds or more</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<list1 type="unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>Sliding roof drive gear sub-assembly (sliding roof control ECU)</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Roof console box assembly (sliding roof control switch)</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>Wire harness</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</content5>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM0000029GH003X_02" type-id="32" category="03" proc-id="RM0250U___0000C5A00000">
<name>WIRING DIAGRAM</name>
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<ptxt>Refer to DTC B2341 (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM0000029GG003X_02"/>).</ptxt>
</content5>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM0000029GH003X_03" type-id="51" category="05">
<name>INSPECTION PROCEDURE</name>
</subpara>
<subpara id="RM0000029GH003X_04" type-id="01" category="01">
<name>PROCEDURE</name>
<testgrp id="RM0000029GH003X_04_0001" proc-id="RM0250U___0000C5B00000">
<testtitle>READ VALUE OF INTELLIGENT TESTER (SLIDE OPEN AND TILT UP SWITCH)</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Use the DATA LIST to check if the sliding roof switch is functioning properly.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Sliding roof ECU</title>
<table pgwide="1">
<tgroup cols="4">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="1.77in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="1.77in"/>
<colspec colname="COL3" colwidth="1.77in"/>
<colspec colname="COL4" align="center" colwidth="1.77in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Item</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Measurement Item/Range (Display)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle" align="center">
<ptxt>Normal Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Diagnostic Note</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>OPEN SW</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Slide switch open signal/ON or OFF</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>ON: OPEN switch is pressed.</ptxt>
<ptxt>OFF: OPEN switch is not pressed.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>-</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>CLOSE SW</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Slide switch close signal/ON or OFF</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>ON: CLOSE switch is pressed.</ptxt>
<ptxt>OFF: CLOSE switch is not pressed.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>-</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>UP SW</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Tilt switch up signal/ON or OFF</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>ON: UP switch is pressed.</ptxt>
<ptxt>OFF: UP switch is not pressed.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>-</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>DOWN SW</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Tilt switch down signal/ON or OFF</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>ON: DOWN switch is pressed.</ptxt>
<ptxt>OFF: DOWN switch is not pressed.</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>-</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
<subtitle>OK</subtitle>
<specitem>
<ptxt>The intelligent tester displays as shown in the table according to the operation of each switch.</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0002" fin="false">OK</down>
<right ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0004" fin="false">NG</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM0000029GH003X_04_0002" proc-id="RM0250U___0000C5C00000">
<testtitle>CHECK SLIDING ROOF FUNCTION</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Check the auto operation with the OPEN, CLOSE, UP and DOWN switches (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000UZX00IX"/>).</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>OK</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>Auto operation operates normally with OPEN, CLOSE, UP and DOWN switches.</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0003" fin="false">OK</down>
<right ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0007" fin="false">NG</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM0000029GH003X_04_0003" proc-id="RM0250U___0000C5D00000">
<testtitle>DELETE DTC</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Delete the DTCs (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000UZP00IX"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0011" fin="true">NEXT</down>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM0000029GH003X_04_0004" proc-id="RM0250U___0000C5E00000">
<testtitle>INSPECT ROOF CONSOLE BOX ASSEMBLY (SLIDING ROOF CONTROL SWITCH)</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Remove the roof console box assembly.</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname="B131165E02" width="2.775699831in" height="4.7836529in"/>
</figure>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>Measure the resistance according to the value(s) in the table below.</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>Standard resistance</title>
<table>
<tgroup cols="3" align="center">
<colspec colname="COL1" colwidth="1.38in"/>
<colspec colname="COL2" colwidth="1.38in"/>
<colspec colname="COL3" colwidth="1.37in"/>
<thead>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Tester Connection</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Switch Position</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Specified Condition</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Q6-1 (CLS) - Q6-3 (GND)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>CLOSE</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Below 100 Ω</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Q6-2 (OPN) - Q6-3 (GND)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>OPEN</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Below 100 Ω</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Q6-4 (DOWN) - Q6-3 (GND)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>DOWN</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Below 100 Ω</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Q6-5 (UP) - Q6-3 (GND)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>UP</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Below 100 Ω</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Q6-1 (CLS) - Q6-3 (GND)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>OPEN</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>1 kΩ or higher</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Q6-2 (OPN) - Q6-3 (GND)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>CLOSE</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>1 kΩ or higher</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Q6-4 (DOWN) - Q6-3 (GND)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>UP</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>1 kΩ or higher</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>Q6-5 (UP) - Q6-3 (GND)</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>DOWN</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry valign="middle">
<ptxt>1 kΩ or higher</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</spec>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0005" fin="false">NG</down>
<right ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0010" fin="false">OK</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM0000029GH003X_04_0005" proc-id="RM0250U___0000C5F00000">
<testtitle>REPLACE ROOF CONSOLE BOX ASSEMBLY (SLIDING ROOF CONTROL SWITCH)</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Temporarily replace the roof console box assembly (sliding roof control switch) with a new one or normally functioning one (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM0000026FZ000X_01_0001"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0006" fin="false">NEXT</down>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM0000029GH003X_04_0006" proc-id="RM0250U___0000C5G00000">
<testtitle>DELETE DTC</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Delete the DTCs (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000UZP00IX"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0011" fin="true">NEXT</down>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM0000029GH003X_04_0007" proc-id="RM0250U___0000C5H00000">
<testtitle>INITIALIZE SLIDING ROOF DRIVE GEAR SUB-ASSEMBLY (SLIDING ROOF CONTROL ECU)</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Check that the sliding roof drive gear sub-assembly can be initialized (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000001VJR003X"/>).</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>OK</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>Sliding roof drive gear sub-assembly can be initialized.</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0008" fin="false">OK</down>
<right ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0010" fin="false">NG</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM0000029GH003X_04_0008" proc-id="RM0250U___0000C5I00000">
<testtitle>CHECK SLIDING ROOF FUNCTION</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Check the auto operation with the OPEN, CLOSE, UP and DOWN switches (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000UZX00IX"/>).</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>OK</title>
<specitem>
<ptxt>Auto operation operates normally with OPEN, CLOSE, UP and DOWN switches.</ptxt>
</specitem>
</spec>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0009" fin="false">OK</down>
<right ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0013" fin="true">NG</right>
</res>
</testgrp>
<testgrp id="RM0000029GH003X_04_0009" proc-id="RM0250U___0000C5J00000">
<testtitle>DELETE DTC</testtitle>
<content6 releasenbr="1">
<test1>
<ptxt>Delete the DTCs (See page <xref label="Seep01" href="RM000000UZP00IX"/>).</ptxt>
</test1>
</content6>
<res>
<down ref="RM0000029GH003X_04_0011" fin="true">NEXT</down>
</res>
</testgrp>
